A simple CodePen-like web application built with React and Tailwind CSS, where you can write HTML, CSS, and JavaScript â€” and see the live output instantly.

Features
Live preview of HTML, CSS, and JS
Auto-update preview with debounce 
Responsive layout 
Styled using Tailwind CSS


How to Run Locally

1) Install dependencies
  npm install

2) Start development server
  npm run dev


Technologies Used
React
Tailwind CSS
Vite (build tool)


